answers.answer: Hi,How are you? Do you have any other symptoms?Some of the causes of facial numbness are diabetes, hyperventilation, excessive anxiety, panic attacks, peripheral neuropathy and nerve compression.I would suggest you do some breathing exercises and get your blood sugar levels checked and see if it improves your symptoms. Take care!
